attributes.description:
This is a first-pass of over 600 items (less than half our inventory) in the store.

Data comes from the "Made In" information on packaging and does not include the second tier information such as where Happy Planet got the bananas for their smoothies.

Suggestions and comments would be greatly appreciated.

Known Bugs:
Strathcona shows up as somewhere just west of Lake Superior!
Some cheese from Quebec is marked as being from Africa!
